name: PickBetween
0:
”Alexa, open Pick Between.”
”Should I eat rice or noodles?”
”Alexa, ask Pick Between if I should play soccer or football.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pick between
des: A fun way to make a hard but non-important decision! For example, if you can't decide what pizza topping you want, or maybe you cant decide whether to play video games or watch YouTube. No worries, Pick Between's got your back. Pick Between is not responsible for the outcome of the choice it makes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
